INSTRUCTIONS:
=============

1. Download Xray-core version 25.10.15 or later from:
   https://github.com/XTLS/Xray-core/releases

2. Look for "Xray-windows-64.zip" (or Xray-windows-32.zip for 32-bit)

3. Extract the archive and locate "xray.exe"

4. Delete this file (<xray_paste_here.exe.txt>)

5. Copy "xray.exe" to this directory (example/windows/xray/)

6. The final structure should be:
   example/
     windows/
       xray/
         xray.exe  <-- Your xray.exe should be here

The plugin will automatically find xray.exe in this location when running the example app.

